=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex7 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 400 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 400.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: -4.1974
  harmonic_regularity: 0.1129
  pitch_clarity: 26.0251
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -8.2665
  resonance_freq: 1162.7930

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 7
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 7 ---
{ LFPulse.ar(LFPulse.kr(LFPulse.kr(0.2,0,0.5,8,10),0,0.5, 400,800),0,0.5,0.1) }.play;
{ LFPulse.ar(LFPulse.kr(3, 0, 0.3, 200, 200), 0, 0.2, 0.1) }.play;
{ LFPulse.ar(XLine.kr(100,15000,6),0,0.5,0.1) }.play;
